[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="EnemyStats" format=3]

; The Overseer: the miniboss that guards the deep room. Everything the poise
; system teaches, examined: crush must be parried or rolled (140 poise), quake
; punishes standing at "safe" range, and the charge closes the gap when you try
; to snipe. Dies rich — the deep room's payoff made flesh.
;
; Reuses the brute's greyscale sheet; the tint IS the identity (ember red vs
; the Brute's purple), same discipline as the rest of the enemy art.

